item.description:
Greetings Incubators!

I apologize for the late notice but there will indeed be an awesome incubator happening tomorrow night at our usual stomping grounds at The Democracy Center in Cambridge.

Come one and come all for some laughs and relaxation. We'll spice things up this week with some new games and lots of other uber fun exercises.

Remems, no improv or acting experience required. So make this your first incubator or make it your 40th.

Any questions? Let me know!

Looking forward to seeing you!

Peace, prosperity, and happiness sent to you all.

Rock on!

Jason
item.name: Tomorrow Never Dings!! well except at Incubator! Come on out tomorrow night!!
